{"tid":1490204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論一下我地還拖嘅武力水平","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T05:04:52.000Z","uid":21961,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"993f40263a4691f839108a0bc524d1c4012e1ac5","tid":1490204,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:54:17.000Z","msg":"呢兩日發生咁多野<br />\n知道勇武手足都不甘於制服佢咁簡單<br />\n即使事後有狗到<br />\n都不外乎即場放/拉完之後唔起訴<br />\n我地還拖唔單單係宣洩我叫地嘅憤怒<br />\n仲要表達一個清楚嘅信息<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>搞鳩我地手足唔係無代價</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n基於以上原因<br />\n所以我覺得有必要討論下還拖武力水平<br />\n例如：<br />\n口角/發現支那蟲 = 言語上屌/影相 （唔郁手）<br />\n無武器郁手 （eg 九龍灣13拳）= 制服佢 索帶綁手 趕佢走<br />\n用武器（刀棍 揸車） = 屈斷手指/爆佢膝蓋 確保佢完全喪失戰鬥力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面可以令我地唔會用過份武力<br />\n同一時間起到保護作用<br />\n所有野我假設<br />\n大家有咩意見歡迎提出"},{"pid":"d7de195baca1bca59fcf846f9a1fbe3375112f2d","tid":1490204,"uid":155292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"最緊要現場會唔會有啲大愛社工出嚟叫大家唔好犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597cc1e577025cb72fe5127df8e5add958bef86a","tid":1490204,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"揸車個d隨時先係最高殺傷力<br />\n班仆街上咗車真係夠膽撞去人<br />\n一定一定要阻佢上返車！"},{"pid":"3b617995c748f031cce8bdc446fdfb224cd748af","tid":1490204,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"對等武力論"},{"pid":"c8a3289de09bad96896184fa15e5d24350359dab","tid":1490204,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7de195baca1bca59fcf846f9a1fbe3375112f2d","tid":1490204,"uid":155292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"最緊要現場會唔會有啲大愛社工出嚟叫大家唔好犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"呢個已經係相對折衷嘅方向<br />\n如果口角就郁手 <br />\n我地真係可能都變成怪獸<br />\n<br />\n同一時間我地知道我地武力去到咩標準<br />\n唔係亂打打死人"},{"pid":"b97ff4fdfc132c3d16474f94a24928c59805363b","tid":1490204,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481490/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481490/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6d825e39f60e491cf4ee87c7a7ab9dab98000e2b","tid":1490204,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b97ff4fdfc132c3d16474f94a24928c59805363b","tid":1490204,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481490/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481490/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"呢個可能係對狗嘅方向<br />\n<br />\n上面我講嘅可能局限咗係對黑社會/廢老"},{"pid":"6bd079c98008dc9b837ffe71f70e14f4a4da07bf","tid":1490204,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"屬於香港既#metoo行動上線啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490165</a><br />\n<br />\n要文宣 要文宣"},{"pid":"c38e2f0329c2621e0e1dc4a0fce20d4c83971d3d","tid":1490204,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d825e39f60e491cf4ee87c7a7ab9dab98000e2b","tid":1490204,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b97ff4fdfc132c3d16474f94a24928c59805363b","tid":1490204,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481490/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481490/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"呢個可能係對狗嘅方向<br />\n<br />\n上面我講嘅可能局限咗係對黑社會/廢老"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"以刀還刀, 以棍還棍"}]}